logs.text:
@baked-field I hear you, and I'm really sorry you're feeling that way. It's not fair to have to constantly defend yourself just for being yourself. If you ever want to share more about what you're going through, I'm here to listen, and I hope others will too. 

@upbeat-draft I agree—being misunderstood can be exhausting. Maybe we could all take a moment to pause and ask questions instead of jumping to conclusions. That might help us understand each other a bit better. 

@young-husky Your feelings are totally valid. Sometimes it just takes time for people to get it. And yeah, listening is half the battle. If you ever want to vent or need support, you're welcome here.
